# Characters
define Taylor = Character("Taylor", color="#c8a2ff")
define Hayden = Character("Hayden", color="#6ec1ff")

# Images for this scene
image bg scene3 = "scene3bg.png"
image Taylor = "taylor.png"
image Hayden = "hayden.png"

label scene3:

    scene bg scene3:
        zoom 1.5

    show Taylor:
        xalign 0.5
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.65

    Taylor "I head back home to check on Hayden. The kid's smart, but there's times I feel he doesn't understand the complexities of situations."

    Taylor "I don't want him attending protests. It's risky enough that I attend them. I can't have him risking his life too."

    Taylor "I'm home."

    show Hayden:
        xalign 0.2
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.75

    show Taylor:
        xalign 0.8
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.65

    Hayden "(panicked) Sis, we gotta go."

    Taylor "The hell you talkin about?"

    Hayden "There were some guys knocking on the door earlier…asking for you."

    Taylor "...Shit. Ok, we need to leave. Pack your bags and leave your phone."

    Hayden "Wait, why?"

    Taylor "First thing they'll track. Can't risk losing you."

    Hayden "Where are we even gonna go, sis?!"

    Taylor "Safehouse. Mom and dad gave me the instructions a while back. Now come on, pack your stuff and let's go before they come back!"

    Hayden "Ok ok! I'm going I'm going!"

    hide Hayden

    show Taylor:
        xalign 0.5
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.65

    Taylor "First the parents, then the kids. Executions really are no joke in this hell."

    Taylor "They have no mercy. Gotta pack my things and get out of here before they find us again."

    Taylor "Ok that's everything. NOW LET'S GET OUT OF HERE!"

    show Hayden:
        xalign 0.2
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.75

    show Taylor:
        xalign 0.8
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.65

    Taylor "Hayden, you ready?"

    Hayden "Yeah! Just grabbing a few more things!"

    Taylor "Alright! Don't forget to put on your mask too!"

    Hayden "Ok ok!"

    hide Hayden

    show Taylor:
        xalign 0.5
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.65

    Taylor "As I grabbed my last item, I rushed to the door and waited for Hayden."

    show Hayden:
        xalign 0.2
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.75

    show Taylor:
        xalign 0.8
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.65

    Hayden "Ok, ok I got everything."

    Taylor "Then let's move. We don't have time to waste!"

    Hayden "I know! I know!"

    hide Hayden

    show Taylor:
        xalign 0.5
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.65

    Taylor "As soon as we had all of our items, we ran out the door."

    Taylor "I looked at the map. A little faded, but it was still legible."

    show Hayden:
        xalign 0.2
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.75

    show Taylor:
        xalign 0.8
        yalign 0.68
        zoom 0.65

    Hayden "How can you even read that thing?!"

    Taylor "I just can. You did leave your phone behind, right?"

    Hayden "(groans) Yes. I did."

    Taylor "Good."

    return